OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777111603
OL,3,CPrince Harry: I will always be part of
OL,4,Cthe Royal Family
OL,6,F'We need to feel empowered to speak
OL,7,Ftruth to power.' On a visit to
OL,8,FUkraine, the Duke of Sussex tells
OL,9,FRoyal Editor Chris Ship that people
OL,10,Fwant to see an end to conflict and
OL,11,Fendless division.
OL,13,FSix years after he left the UK with
OL,14,FMeghan, Prince Harry has said he will
OL,15,F"always be part of the Royal Family".
OL,17,FThe Duke of Sussex has been speaking
OL,18,Fto ITV News at the end of a two-day
OL,19,Fvisit to Ukraine, in which he appears
OL,20,Fto be more confident to speak out on
OL,21,Fissues about which he feels strongly.
OL,26,@wD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777111603
OL,3,CPrince Harry: I will always be part of
OL,4,Cthe Royal Family
OL,6,F"I am here working doing the things
OL,7,Fthat I was born to do", he said, "And
OL,8,FI enjoy doing it."
OL,10,FHe had travelled an hour's drive from
OL,11,Fthe capital Kyiv on Friday to a town
OL,12,Fwhich is now synonymous with a war
OL,13,Fcrime.
OL,15,FIn Bucha, four years ago, Russian
OL,16,Fforces are accused of committing war
OL,17,Fcrimes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@VO]oD@bOUpD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777111603
OL,3,CPrince Harry: I will always be part of
OL,4,Cthe Royal Family
OL,6,FFive hundred people were murdered and
OL,7,Fexecuted in the town during a month-
OL,8,Flong Russian occupation, before
OL,9,FUkrainian forces retook the area.
OL,11,FAs they did so, the troops made the
OL,12,Fgrim discovery of what had happened to
OL,13,Fmany civilians here.
OL,15,FAnd when issues are as big as this,
OL,16,FPrince Harry appears to have decided
OL,17,Fhe can be bolder when it comes to
OL,18,Fspeaking about some world events.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777111603
OL,3,CPrince Harry: I will always be part of
OL,4,Cthe Royal Family
OL,6,FWhen we asked if he feels like the
OL,7,Fshackles have been removed after the
OL,8,FDuke and Duchess of Sussex quit as
OL,9,Fworking royals in 2020, he said: "From
OL,10,Fmy perspective, we need to feel
OL,11,Fempowered to speak truth to power.
OL,12,FIt's really that simple."
OL,14,F"What would worry me if we live in a
OL,15,Fworld where anyone in my position or
OL,16,Fanybody, anywhere can't speak about
OL,17,Fthe very things and the realities that
OL,18,Fwe are seeing", he told us.
OL,26,@tD@YO]vD@AOUzD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777111603
OL,3,CPrince Harry: I will always be part of
OL,4,Cthe Royal Family
OL,6,FHe didn't want to feel "gagged", he
OL,7,Fsaid, because everything is considered
OL,8,Ftoo political.
OL,10,F"I fundamentally disagree with that."
OL,12,FHe was talking to us from St Andrew's
OL,13,FChurch in Bucha, the site of a mass
OL,14,Fgrave in 2022, and where there is now
OL,15,Fa memorial for the 500 civilians
OL,16,Fkilled here.
OL,18,FI followed his speech on Thursday at
OL,19,Fthe Kyiv Security Forum, calling
OL,20,FPresident Putin by name, urging him to
OL,21,Fstop the war.
OL,26,@nD@XOUnD@_O]rD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
