OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777111603
OL,3,CPrince Harry: I will always be part of
OL,4,Cthe Royal Family
OL,6,FHarry said: "I will always be part of
OL,7,Fthe Royal Family, and I am here
OL,8,Fworking doing the things that I was
OL,9,Fborn to do. And I enjoy doing it."
OL,11,FHe also spoke about his mother,
OL,12,FPrincess Diana, as he drove into a
OL,13,Fwood in the early morning to see the
OL,14,Fwork of the de-mining charity, The
OL,15,FHalo Trust.
OL,26,@qD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777111603
OL,3,CPrince Harry: I will always be part of
OL,4,Cthe Royal Family
OL,6,FThe images of the late princess
OL,7,Fwalking through a minefield in Angola
OL,8,Fin 1997 changed the way the world saw
OL,9,Fthe issue of landmines - and the
OL,10,Fimpact they have had for decades
OL,11,Fafterwards on civilians.
OL,13,FThe Halo Trust means so much to Harry,
OL,14,Fbecause - as he told us today - it
OL,15,Fmeant so much to his mother.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1777111603
OL,3,CPrince Harry: I will always be part of
OL,4,Cthe Royal Family
OL,6,F"It's sad, it's very, very sad because
OL,7,Fnearly 30 years ago, since my mother
OL,8,Fwas in Angola, here we are again in a
OL,9,Fnew conflict", Harry said after seeing
OL,10,Fthe work to remove Russian ammunition
OL,11,Fand other ordnance from a former
OL,12,Fbattlefield near Bucha.
OL,14,FHe added: "It's sad, it's depressing,
OL,15,Fbut thank God for Halo Trust."
OL,17,FWhat Harry says he wants to do more
OL,18,Fnow is to use his platform to bring
OL,19,Fattention to issues, like those he has
OL,20,Fspoken about in Ukraine, that have
OL,21,Ffallen off the world's news agenda.
OL,26,@qD@MO]wD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
