OL,3,CPrince Harry: I will always be part of
OL,4,Cthe Royal Family
OL,6,FThe Iran war has taken a lot of the
OL,7,Fattention away from Ukraine in recent
OL,8,Fmonths.
OL,10,FSo was this a Royal tour or not royal
OL,11,Ftour? With the Sussexes, everyone
OL,12,Falways has an opinion.
OL,14,FOn certain issues, however, military
OL,15,Fones in particular, Harry appears to
OL,16,Fbe done with the tiptoeing around.
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
